Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO + VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 4
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Fame, romance and broken hearts. In this installment, resentment causes problems on set.
Title: SKIP BEAT, VOL. 23
Author: Yoshiki Nakamura

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 1
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: After the death of her brother, Teru Kurebayashi has been receiving comforting messages from Daisy, who communicates through her brother’s cell phone. In this installment, she learns Daisy’s identity.
Title: DENGEKI DAISY, VOL. 4
Author: Kyousuke Motomi

Description: Naruto, ninja in training, learns more about his destiny and the fate of his universe.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 50
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: More hi jinks for poor Sumi, who secretly married for money and is trying to pass herself off as a true member of high society.
Title: STEPPING ON ROSES, VOL. 5
Author: Rinko Ueda

Description: The destiny of Sakura, the princess of a moon kingdom and who is fated to wield a legendary sword, begins here.
Title: SAKURA HIME: THE LEGEND OF PRINCESS SAKURA, VOL. 1
Author: Arina Tanemura

Description: Rikuo Nura is part human, part supernatural creature. But his future awaits: to be the leader of a demon clan.
Title: NURA, VOL. 2
Author: Hiroshi Shiibashi

Description: The next generation of Yu-Gi-Oh battle it out at the Duel Academy. But what evil plans are afoot?
Title: YU-GI-OH! GX, VOL. 6
Author: Naoyuki Kageyama

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human? In this volume: butler vs. butler!
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 4
Author: Yana Toboso
